cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Your double was good Stan. It is hard to make the perfect decision on these auctions. I probably would have done the same thing. But hands with voids are "magic" and often are worth 2 tricks or more than even hands with singletons. |
PG| ***** 84 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So whenever you have a void in the opponent's suit, it is right to be super aggressive. If you go down 2 you are ahead if we make 5@H. But behind if we don't. I think most experts would double with Stan. But I don't know. these hands are hard.|
